OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA largely cloudy day with
OL,6,Fpatchy rain or showers. Occasional
OL,7,Fbrighter breaks developing in the
OL,8,Fsouth by the afternoon. Somewhat less
OL,9,Fmild but winds generally light.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FDrier by the evening
OL,12,Finitially with clear skies. Turning
OL,13,Fcloudier again with outbreaks of rain
OL,14,Fand a freshening breezy. Remaining
OL,15,Fgenerally frost-free.
OL,16,
OL,17,CSunday:FCloudy with outbreaks of rain
OL,18,Fand drizzle, most persistent through
OL,19,Fthe morning and turning heavy at times
OL,20,Fover the hills. Breezy and mild.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
